Program: Discovery
Title: The science of selling - part two
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz38
Last Broadcast Date: 31 January 2006
A look at the everyday items we take for granted. The programme examines branding and how an item or services associations with buyers must 'get into their psyche' in order to sell something to someone. What makes one brand more important than another? How would a leading advertising agency sell the BBC World Service? Show less